dct_description_sm: This tabular data, prepared by Data You Can Use, presents the share of households without a grocery store within 1/2 mile by census tract in the city of Milwaukee, Wisconsin. The data is sourced from the 2019 Food Research Atlas prepared by the Economic Research Service (USDA) and utilizes 2020 Census tracts. For more information, please visit Data You Can Use.
